<h2 class="text-3xl text-teal-900 font-bold my-4">
    <strong>Ice Fishing: Is It Possible Near Portland?</strong>
</h2>
<p class="mb-4">
    While Portland itself doesn’t see much ice, some nearby mountain lakes can freeze in colder winters.
</p>
<h3>
    <strong>Top Ice Fishing Options</strong>
</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
